                   energy release is in the region of 50 erg cm-3 to
                   avoid unphysical magnetic field strengths; (5) the
                   heating timescale may be short for loops of total
                   length less than 40 Mm to be consistent with the
                   observed range of slopes; (6) predicted slopes are
